1:16:11.708 --> 1:16:14.291
[audience applauds]

1:16:17.000 --> 1:16:19.500
[traditional music continues]

1:16:50.041 --> 1:16:53.458
[audience applauds and cheers]

1:17:01.208 --> 1:17:03.625
