1:17:22.541 --> 1:17:24.291
I'm not gonna puke or anything.

1:17:24.916 --> 1:17:25.750
Okay.

1:17:26.333 --> 1:17:27.750
[Alex] Oh, it's been amazing--

1:17:27.833 --> 1:17:29.125
Sinh.

1:17:29.208 --> 1:17:30.583
Sinh?

1:17:30.666 --> 1:17:32.791
My dad sold the tour company.

1:17:32.875 --> 1:17:34.791
Your dad sold Saigon Silver Star?

1:17:36.291 --> 1:17:37.500
To who?

1:17:37.583 --> 1:17:41.083
An American company called Tourista?

1:17:41.166 --> 1:17:42.291
Ah--!

1:17:42.375 --> 1:17:45.333
Amanda, why didn't you tell me?

1:17:46.041 --> 1:17:47.125
Why would she know?

1:17:50.416 --> 1:17:51.250
Uh…

1:17:51.333 --> 1:17:52.875
-I'm sorry. No, I'm--
-I'm…

1:17:54.333 --> 1:17:56.666
[Amanda] Uh… [clears throat]

1:17:56.750 --> 1:17:58.083
I'm a…

1:17:59.375 --> 1:18:01.750
I'm a travel executive with Tourista,

1:18:01.833 --> 1:18:04.125
and it is not what it looks like.

1:18:04.208 --> 1:18:06.208
I mean, it is, but it's not,

1:18:06.291 --> 1:18:08.666
and also, I can explain, all right? So…

1:18:09.875 --> 1:18:11.541
Sinh? Sinh.

1:18:12.750 --> 1:18:15.000
Sinh! Sinh!

1:18:16.500 --> 1:18:18.458
So this was all just business?

1:18:18.541 --> 1:18:20.291
Sure, it started that way,

1:18:20.375 --> 1:18:23.291
it did, but I had the trip of a lifetime.

1:18:23.375 --> 1:18:25.791
And all I want
is for other people to experience that.

1:18:25.875 --> 1:18:28.666
Why would I believe
anything you say now? Huh?

1:18:30.416 --> 1:18:33.750
-I feel like such an idiot.
-No, no, I am the idiot. I am the idiot.

1:18:33.833 --> 1:18:35.666
I wanted to come clean and tell you,

1:18:35.750 --> 1:18:38.250
-but I didn't know if it was gonna happen.
-Stop.

1:18:39.000 --> 1:18:39.833
Just stop.

1:18:42.833 --> 1:18:44.250
What does it matter now?

1:18:48.666 --> 1:18:49.666
[gasps]

1:18:51.958 --> 1:18:56.041
[bittersweet music playing]

1:18:57.750 --> 1:19:00.500
[John] I mean,
aside from the Tourista drama,

1:19:00.583 --> 1:19:02.291
last night was so much fun.

1:19:02.375 --> 1:19:06.166
You know, the puppets and the crazy food
on the tiny little chairs.

1:19:06.250 --> 1:19:09.875
Everything's so authentic
and adorable here.

1:19:10.416 --> 1:19:13.583
But the best part was being here with you,

1:19:14.666 --> 1:19:17.708
which is lucky for me

1:19:18.250 --> 1:19:21.250
because Reed only needs me
'til the end of the year.

1:19:22.041 --> 1:19:25.333
So, we just do long-distance 'til then,

1:19:25.416 --> 1:19:26.625
I'm back in LA,

1:19:26.708 --> 1:19:31.708
and we can start… looking for houses

1:19:31.791 --> 1:19:33.916
like you, uh… like you keep wanting to.

1:19:34.833 --> 1:19:35.958
House hunting?

1:19:36.583 --> 1:19:39.875
I think that's quite a turnaround,
because two weeks ago,

1:19:39.958 --> 1:19:42.833
-you were excited to be on a hiatus.
-[scoffs]

1:19:43.833 --> 1:19:44.666
Yeah, no, I--

1:19:44.750 --> 1:19:48.208
Look-- I mean,
I would pay a fortune to take that back.

1:19:48.291 --> 1:19:51.500
But you can't and you shouldn't because

1:19:52.416 --> 1:19:53.791
we are where we are.

1:19:53.875 --> 1:19:54.833
Exactly.

1:19:54.916 --> 1:19:55.833
Here.

1:19:56.708 --> 1:20:01.166
It's funny, I think I was so horrified
by the idea of marriage

1:20:01.250 --> 1:20:06.083
that I ran all the way to Ohio
just to avoid it, but then I realized,

1:20:06.166 --> 1:20:09.458
if it's that important to you,
I should be willing to make the sacrifice.

1:20:09.541 --> 1:20:11.916
But it shouldn't be a sacrifice, John.

1:20:12.000 --> 1:20:15.541
Look, if you wanted to be with me,
it wouldn't even feel like a compromise.

1:20:15.625 --> 1:20:18.833
Hell, if you wanted to be with me,
you would have asked me to move to Ohio.

1:20:23.625 --> 1:20:24.625
Look.

1:20:26.166 --> 1:20:28.000
When you left, I was lost.

1:20:29.000 --> 1:20:31.958
I was so comfortable
in our little corner of the world

1:20:32.041 --> 1:20:34.375
that I never bothered
to look around outside of it.

1:20:36.458 --> 1:20:40.958
And as deeply corny as it sounds,
this trip has shown me that

1:20:42.208 --> 1:20:44.125
I wasn't actually lost, I just…

1:20:45.541 --> 1:20:47.625
I just wasn't where I was supposed to be.

1:20:49.416 --> 1:20:50.666
