1:20:52.833 --> 1:20:53.833
It's, uh…

1:20:56.125 --> 1:20:59.708
This feels like
it could have been an email.

1:20:59.791 --> 1:21:01.041
[Amanda chuckles]

1:21:02.916 --> 1:21:05.000
Possibly, yeah, but, uh…

1:21:06.458 --> 1:21:10.125
[sighs] You know, I'm…
I'm so glad you're here.

1:21:10.208 --> 1:21:11.708
I really am, truly,

1:21:11.791 --> 1:21:15.875
