this conversation with you through a door

1:21:15.958 --> 1:21:21.583
or over email because five years
deserves better than that.

1:21:22.916 --> 1:21:23.750
Yeah.

1:21:24.958 --> 1:21:25.791
Yeah, it does.

1:21:30.125 --> 1:21:30.958
[sighs]

1:21:31.041 --> 1:21:32.416
