1:21:32.500 --> 1:21:35.500
I, uh… I should--

1:21:36.958 --> 1:21:38.958
probably book a flight home,

1:21:39.500 --> 1:21:41.541
and fast, you know,

1:21:41.625 --> 1:21:45.916
before I'm sitting in the middle seat
for 20 hours.

1:21:50.083 --> 1:21:53.500
