1:22:35.875 --> 1:22:38.458
Look, I was chicken.

1:22:39.875 --> 1:22:41.333
That's not like you.

1:22:41.416 --> 1:22:43.125
I worry about my job too.

1:22:44.041 --> 1:22:47.041
