1:23:09.500 --> 1:23:11.125
My dreams for the company.

1:23:15.583 --> 1:23:16.416
Amanda.

1:23:17.750 --> 1:23:19.791
Why are you giving up so easily?

1:23:22.208 --> 1:23:26.250
[in Vietnamese] I thought the new year
would bring meaningful changes, but--

1:23:31.958 --> 1:23:36.291
