you've ever taken?

1:24:08.625 --> 1:24:09.500
Yes!

1:24:09.583 --> 1:24:10.958
By far.

1:24:11.041 --> 1:24:15.666
I just-- I felt like I was truly
in the middle of it all, you know?

1:24:15.750 --> 1:24:19.583
Like we had a very authentic
cultural experience,

1:24:19.666 --> 1:24:23.708
